primary.context: Customer wanted to verify the address and ownership on file for their maintenance bill.
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and provided the address and owner name on file.

steps: Agent identified the bill type as maintenance.
Agent performed account lookup via phone number.
Agent verified caller using name and state.
Agent provided address on file upon request.
Agent provided owner name on file upon request.
Caller confirmed no further assistance was needed.

clarifications.note: Agent asked for spelling when name didn't match.

corrections.note: User corrected first name from Vincent to Valerie.

actions.detail: Verified Valerie Creo in New Jersey.

insights.summary: The customer successfully verified their account and obtained address and ownership information related to their maintenance bill. The AI handled the name discrepancy smoothly and fulfilled all requests.
